Third-party boundary notice

MediaCrawler (https://github.com/NanmiCoder/MediaCrawler) is NOT part of this
software and is NOT distributed with it. `infinance setup` fetches a pinned
checkout onto the user's own machine, where it runs under its own
non-commercial / learning license. infinance talks to it only over its
command-line interface and never bundles, imports, or redistributes it.
Keep crawl volumes personal and modest; see docs/account-safety.md.
